INSERT INTO `featured_week` VALUES (1,60,'Kickin\' It Off with Sneaker Week!','','',''),(2,61,'PEZ Pride: More Than Just Candy','','',''),(3,18,'Meet Anyango and  Her Jungle Love','','',''),(4,63,'Clothing, Cars and Cuties. What More Could a Doll Want?','Doll Videos','Seriously, the girl has everything. Even new careers each year. Take a look at our gorgeous girl on parade. At least you don\'t have to wear those heels.','10736'),(5,64,'Built Like a Brickhouse and Driving Boys Crazy','','Didn\'t everyone want to be a Lego Engineer growing up? The blocks hold a certain nostalgia for most and this week we prove that it is not just the kids getting in on the action.',''),(6,65,'Animal Week: And I Went to the Four Legged Zoo','','Noah really must have had his hands full. At least our collectors don\'t have to pay for the hay.',''),(7,66,'Homage to Princess Diana','Justice League','Wonder Woman has always represented a strong, free- spirited woman. Furthermore, the gal has her own private plane and still looks great in a bodysuit.',''),(8,67,'There\'s No Place Like Home','','Sitting at a game is a sensory overload â€“ the smells, the sounds, the colors of fans emanating from the stands. This weekâ€™s showcase is  how to take a little piece of nostalgia back home.',''),(9,285,'Baby You Can Drive My Car','Car Related Videos','You too can bring one of these babies home without worrying about the parking space or those damn idiots who drive just a little too close. The only thing that is missing is that new car smell.','11753'),(10,101,'It\'s Not Easy Being Green. Or Extinct For That Matter.','','Dinosaurs rock. You know you want one. Mom said if we walk and feed it. Ok, she didn\'t say a dinosaur specifically but we believe in our hearts that is what she meant.',''),(11,1,'Wham! Bam! Thank You Ma\'am!','Action Figure/Comic Related Videos','The age-old dilemma: to box or not to box? The solution: buying two - one to play with and one to keep pristine in the plastic. We just hate to think some of those toys are missing out on the action.',''),(12,34,'Records  Week','The Passionate Record Collector','With the omnipresent mp3, it\'s nice to get to feel a little vinyl every now and then. Not to mention the sound still beats the digital format any day.',''),(13,115,' Meet Danny McCormick','','Collectors\' Quest wants to do its part in supporting the arts by adding Artist Weeks in our mix. After all, today\'s street artist can be tomorrow\'s collectible.',''),(14,752,'Record Week: You Spin Me Right Round','The Passionate Record Collector','With the omnipresent mp3, it\'s nice to get to feel a little vinyl every now and then. Not to mention the sound still beats the digital format any day.',''),(15,50,'Let it snow! Let it snow! Let it snow!','','Living life in a bubble is not such a bad thing, if you can find residence in a snowdome. Maybe your house is a little smaller but your holidays will always be white.',''),(16,753,'Thank You, Thank You Very Much...','','Elvis would be 74 this week. King or no King, he still looks damn good for an international icon. ',''),(18,333,'Artist of the Week: Ted Stanke','','Collectors\' Quest wants to do its part in supporting the arts and as such we are now premiering Artist Weeks in our mix. After all, today\'s street artist can be tomorrow\'s collectible.',''),(20,245,'Coin Week:  Money, That\'s What I Want','','Money makes the world go \'round. This week CQ takes you on a trip across the world and into the pockets of some proud coin collectors.',''),(21,755,'Black Action Figures: Short, Dark and Handsome','Action Figure Videos','In honor of Black History Month, we wanted to show the world that even action figures are changing, representing new leaps and bounds in the toy arena.',''),(22,756,'I\'m Too Sexy for My Slip','','Valentine\'s Day is just around the corner. CQ premieres some lacy collections that are sure to get your heart pumping.',''),(23,757,'Happy Birthday,  Mr. Pres-i-dent! ','','This week we celebrate President\'s Day and it\'s politics as usual. Well, we guess it depends what side you\'re on. For these collectors, it depends what button you\'re on.',''),(24,184,'Take One Down, Pass It Around...','','In honor of Mardi Gras, we have decided to celebrate Beer Week, because where there are lots of beads, there is lots of beer.',''),(25,758,'The Toys Are Back In Town','','What kid didn\'t love Hot Wheels? The fact that you can make a sweet ramp off of a staircase and store hundreds of cars without the need for a Jerry Seinfeld size garage, only adds to their appeal.',''),(26,235,'If I Could Turn Back Time...','','Is it just us or is everyone still missing that hour of sleep? At the collectors\' homes this week, we can at least pretend we have time on our side.','17539'),(27,305,'CQ Phone Home','','In celebration of a number of telecommunication breakthroughs this month, we bring you Phone Week. And a reminder to call your Mom.',''),(28,44,'No Matching Shoes Required','','Girls night out seems to be more common these days. With gorgeous bags like these can you really blame the ladies?','17977'),(29,313,'Venture Forth, Halflings!','','Join us on our quest into a mythical world of fairies, elves and dragons -- and stay away from the pixie dust.',''),(30,269,'Which Came First?','','Go beyond the Easter scope with our featured eggers. Hopefully, these unique art works will never have to go through any Humpty Dumpty type trauma. ',''),(31,759,'We\'re Not Duckin\' Around','','These ain\'t your grandma\'s rubber ducks! This week we\'re featuring everyone\'s favorite bath time toy. Endless ducks jokes will ensue.',''),(32,760,'Magnet Week: I Find You Oddly Attractive...','','Drawn to this feature are you? This week\'s collections  remain truly magnetic while reminding you that you are out of milk.','20412'),(33,335,'Vivienne Strauss','','Think twice before you throw away that old magazine. Vivienne Strauss takes some cues from Dadaists to create a new spin on the term copy and paste.',''),(34,764,'Hakuna Matata!','','CQ is a jungle...a mighty jungle of awesome collectors. This week we are a month away from the 15 year anniversary of the release Disney\'s \"The Lion King\" . Come in and check out our pride!',''),(35,280,'The Original Dynamic Duo','','CQ is shaking it up with salt and pepper shaker week! Take a look at how our featured collectors spice up their lives.',''),(36,252,'I Think I\'m Turning Japanese...','','This week we\'re off to the land of the rising sun. We\'re featuring some collections that are so huge, they can probably form a road that will take us all the way to Japan!',''),(37,30,'Hup 2,3,4...','','Atteeeention! We\'re saluting the troops this week with a wide range of militaria collections. War! What is it good for? Absolute collecting!',''),(38,766,'Mom Warned Me About These Creeps...','','Beware, guys and ghouls! We reached into the dark depths of the internet underworld and have brought you the scariest collections out there. There\'s no turning back now... ',''),(39,26,'What\'s Cookin\' ?','','CQ is stirring up the week with kitchenalia collectors. If you can\'t stand the heat, get out of the kitchen!',''),(40,765,'Good To The Last Crumb','','This week we are featuring some cookie jar crazed collectors! Check out all the fun ways Mom kept these delicious treats out of your reach. Hey - did you finish your dinner?',''),(41,370,'Put A Lid On It','','For over 90 years,  Pyrex has helped make family dinners a colorful affair. Take a look at these vibrant collections that even make brussel sprouts look appetizing.',''),(42,767,'Strike A Pose...','','Say cheese! This week we\'re featuring collectors who love to point and shoot for interesting cameras. They\'re ready for their close-up!',''),(43,768,'The Way He Makes Us Feel','','This week we are paying tribute to the King of Pop: Michael Jackson. He is seen as an icon all over the world. We are celebrating his life by showing some fan collections.',''),(44,3